(87, 4, '2015-08-28 11:29:32', '2015-08-28 19:29:32', '<div class="hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg visible-xs banner_text">supply chain corruption is a serious issue and requires robust controls</div>\r\n<h1>Anti-Corruption</h1>\r\n<p class="highlight">Fraud and corruption across supply chains is a serious risk and has enormous potential consequences to your business. Common corrupt practices include purchase orders being awarded to poorly qualified suppliers, factories with egregious ethical issues becoming part of your supply chain or defective shipments being passed by quality inspectors.</p>\r\nWhile these risks can never be eliminated it is imperative that you have the requisite controls in place across your business operations. Omega‚Äôs dedicated ethical monitoring team provides a broad range of integrity investigations services, such as conflicts of interest, bribery, and fraud, both internal and external, to companies who may not have the in-house resources to manage this risk themselves. Omega has unparalleled experience in developing and managing anti-corruption programs, programs which span more than 20 countries and a supply base in excess of 2,000 manufacturers.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="https://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Anti-Corruption', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-28 11:29:32', '2015-08-28 19:29:32', '', 41, 'https://local.omega.com/41-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
