(132, 4, '2015-09-07 20:02:35', '2015-09-08 04:02:35', '<h1>Inspections</h1>\r\n<p class="highlight">Relying on in-house factory inspections can be a risk. Too often merchandise received is of inferior quality, incorrectly packaged, incorrectly labeled or short shipped.</p>\r\nWith supply chains stretching across the globe, the time required to return the merchandise, process a claim and allow vendors to rework orders can cost significant retail dollars.\r\n\r\nOmega provides you with comprehensive quality inspection services. Our 3rd party inspection teams are on the front line, working at your manufacturers, striving to assure that the goods you receive meet your exacting requirements.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="https://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Inspections', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '39-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-07 20:02:35', '2015-09-08 04:02:35', '', 39, 'https://local.omega.com/39-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
