e countries can be daunting. Omega has vast experience dealing with supply chain integrity risks. For more information on how Omega can support your business, please contact us.', 'How Do I Prevent Bribery Across My Supply Base?', 'Consumer brands and retailers have clear regulations governing unethical supply chain practices within their own organizations.¬† Should an allegation of corrupt practices about an associate be substantiated, an established set of procedures are followed usually leading to termination or even prosecution. ¬†', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '254-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-27 22:18:33', '2016-01-28 06:18:33', '', 254, 'https://local.omega.com/254-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
