(491, 4, '2017-02-28 20:56:49', '2017-03-01 04:56:49', 'While these risks can never be eliminated it is imperative that you have the requisite controls in place across your business operations. Omega‚Äôs dedicated ethical monitoring team provides a broad range of integrity investigations services, such as conflicts of interest, bribery, and fraud, both internal and external, to companies who may not have the in-house resources to manage this risk themselves. Omega has unparalleled experience in developing and managing anti-corruption programs, programs which span more than 20 countries and a supply base in excess of 2,000 manufacturers.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="https://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Integrity', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-28 20:56:49', '2017-03-01 04:56:49', '', 41, 'http://local.omega.com/41-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(492, 4, '2017-02-28 20:57:54', '2017-03-01 04:57:54', 'Leveraging our extensive remediation expertise, we operate our own proprietary training programs in which our expert social compliance and factory security teams will educate your vendors in the requisite procedures to ensure minimum standards are met.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href="https://local.omega.com/contact/">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Training', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-28 20:57:54', '2017-03-01 04:57:54', '', 43, 'http://local.omega.com/43-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
